Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.05,0:00:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.15,0:00:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翌晨的陽光就快來臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.25,0:00:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照進這間充滿煙蒂\N雜亂無章的屋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.13,0:00:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why 聖母瑪利亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.30,0:00:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對溫柔感到飢渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.37,0:00:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me why
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.21,0:00:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼孤單的夜晚\N總是如此漫長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.08,0:00:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牛仔褲下的膝蓋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.88,0:00:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被破碎的夢想打溼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.29,0:01:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿著襯衫的胸部太過耀眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.26,0:01:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.55,0:01:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有生以來第一次\N被男人抱在懷裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.49,0:01:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.92,0:01:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟著他一輩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.31,0:01:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.38,0:01:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然抱住那個愛狗的女孩\N這是我這輩子最大的失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.02,0:02:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.96,0:02:08.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,叔叔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.36,0:02:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還躺在床上啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.26,0:02:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼搞的\N健康不是你最自豪的優點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.93,0:02:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為那些小狗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.27,0:02:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我請明日菜來探病吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.74,0:02:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要這樣!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.44,0:02:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不想被心愛的女人看到\N自己憔悴的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.51,0:02:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這種時候正可以培養愛情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.81,0:02:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,探什麼病嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.32,0:02:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔,探病啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.32,0:02:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#60看見了!\N響子和三鷹突然上了二壘?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.03,0:02:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜,妳有沒有在聽?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.14,0:02:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹的身體果然很差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.08,0:02:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼?又病倒啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.98,0:03:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊\N上次約了明日菜開車出去兜風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果半路突然身體不適
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.25,0:03:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還叫計程車把明日菜送回來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.82,0:03:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.86,0:03:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得他是個好人,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說從那天之後\N他就一直病倒在床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.60,0:03:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看這樁婚事還是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊,他病倒在床上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是音無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.08,0:03:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,我現在在家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道妳過得好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.12,0:03:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你生病了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.03,0:03:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,這幾天都躺在床上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.26,0:03:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.23,0:03:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳一定很忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.30,0:03:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.24,0:03:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我不打擾妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.70,0:04:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.91,0:04:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想聽聽妳的聲音而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.34,0:04:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個人住,又病倒在床上的話\N總會倍感寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.95,0:04:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有按時吃飯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.32,0:04:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,這幾天都湊合著隨便吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.69,0:04:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我過去看看你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.92,0:04:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會,我不忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.33,0:04:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼需要的東西嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.46,0:04:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我明天就去看你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.57,0:04:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了進退兩難的地步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.91,0:04:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹當然會逼問她求婚的回覆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.88,0:04:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員應該明知道這點才去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有沒有在聽啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.29,0:04:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天曉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.20,0:05:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.67,0:05:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.47,0:05:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快中午了,你不用去幼稚園嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.01,0:05:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我今天請假了\N總覺得有點累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是年紀大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用裝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.45,0:05:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一副落寞憔悴的臉\N沒必要硬擠出笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.26,0:06:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳要去啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.46,0:06:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家裡拜託妳看一下\N我會儘早回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,妳去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.01,0:06:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乖喔,好乖好乖喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬一他留我下來的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.57,0:08:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.30,0:08:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思,大門沒鎖\N請自己進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.65,0:08:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我看錯了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.29,0:08:44.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,真是不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛去刮鬍子\N所以還穿著睡衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.43,0:08:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來,請進吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.53,0:08:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,我到這裡就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.47,0:09:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是便當…雖然做的不太好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.61,0:09:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想逃避嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.56,0:09:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.69,0:09:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跑來這裡幹嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先生…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.23,0:09:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問你有沒有看到小狗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.40,0:09:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一隻小小的博美狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.77,0:09:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小狗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.27,0:09:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,一個不留神,牠就…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我沒看到…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.78,0:09:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來,管理員進去的時候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.19,0:09:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是如果不那麼說的話\N似乎沒有辦法把妳留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.46,0:10:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我,真的快被逼瘋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.57,0:10:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為某些陰錯陽差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.17,0:10:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相親的對象反而更喜歡我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照這樣下去的話,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.89,0:10:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.79,0:10:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.03,0:10:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位小姐真的來這裡了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.14,0:10:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.07,0:10:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.88,0:10:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求妳,請妳轉過身來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.61,0:10:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.36,0:10:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.46,0:11:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.37,0:11:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是莎拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.35,0:12:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.58,0:12:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代怎麼會來這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.56,0:12:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳找到小狗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.06,0:12:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的幫忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.67,0:12:51.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要把我嚇死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.40,0:12:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然坐賓士來找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.77,0:12:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位千金小姐是誰?\N你的新馬子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.08,0:13:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.71,0:13:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你根本沒有這種本事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.97,0:13:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失戀啦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的失戀了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.40,0:13:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得解釋才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要解釋清楚\N五代一定會諒解的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.50,0:14:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.17,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.74,0:14:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽叫我拿這個來還妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝,辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.49,0:14:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦?賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.76,0:14:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員看起來怎麼樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.74,0:14:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,好像沒什麼精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.51,0:14:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪了\N在三鷹家出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.05,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拒絕了他的求婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.25,0:14:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那五代就有希望了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.15,0:14:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼重要的時候\N他在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.29,0:15:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,椎實幼稚園你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.79,0:15:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?五代?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.02,0:15:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代今天還沒來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.39,0:15:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊\N好,謝謝妳,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.10,0:15:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,借妳的洗衣機用一下喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己開來用了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.87,0:16:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說\N你要不吃不睡,都是你的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.61,0:16:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,不要這樣愁眉苦臉的好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.92,0:16:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是阪本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.72,0:16:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,管理員啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.66,0:16:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代?這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.56,0:16:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫我跟妳說,他不在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.13,0:16:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你傳話給他,叫他快點回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.77,0:16:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他說他回來之後\N我會跟他解釋清楚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.67,0:16:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他果然誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.52,0:17:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦!不要啦!\N我不要回一刻館!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.86,0:17:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰說要帶你回一刻館了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.89,0:17:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.56,0:17:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回不回一刻館是你的自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.03,0:17:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過,一直悶在房子裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.64,0:17:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋和身體都會爛掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.14,0:17:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出去動動身體啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不好?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直躲起來也不是辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.75,0:17:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.32,0:17:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說得對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.69,0:17:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是失戀而已嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.03,0:17:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搬離那個地方,忘掉她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快來,快來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.41,0:18:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看,好高好高喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,接下來換誰呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.95,0:18:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.39,0:18:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照順序來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.75,0:18:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.79,0:18:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇,好高喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.42,0:18:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.70,0:18:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說管理員和三鷹終於訂婚了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.27,0:18:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,妳是聽誰說的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.04,0:18:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天你出門之後,我去了一刻館
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.91,0:18:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後一之瀨太太跟我說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.62,0:18:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.95,0:18:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一之瀨太太本來就是個大嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.09,0:18:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,我問你喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.66,0:18:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實你有點喜歡管理員\N對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.34,0:19:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.97,0:19:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她長得漂亮,人又溫柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.04,0:19:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且很會照顧人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.11,0:19:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我受到她很多照顧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.48,0:19:13.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就像姊姊的感覺嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.75,0:19:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.89,0:19:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人一生當中\N總會喜歡一次年紀大的女生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.24,0:20:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會今晚也不打算回來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.08,0:20:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.51,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總是誤會來誤會去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.32,0:20:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你說…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.64,0:20:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.41,0:20:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.64,0:20:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個人還真壞\N有什麼好隱瞞的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.91,0:20:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也幫我跟三鷹說聲對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.96,0:21:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.83,0:21:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.17,0:21:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.60,0:21:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你聽我說,關於那件事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.17,0:21:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.51,0:21:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那件事我一點都不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.71,0:21:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不好意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.28,0:21:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早知道你們是那種關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.52,0:21:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不會去三鷹他家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.65,0:21:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前我也不是故意讓妳為難的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.62,0:21:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我早點知道的話\N早點知道的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.56,0:21:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼啊\N五代,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.83,0:21:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起,我覺得自己很丟臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.80,0:21:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請妳讓我一個人靜一靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.24,0:21:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代,事情不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.77,0:21:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是三鷹單方面的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.28,0:21:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.98,0:21:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經死心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.48,0:21:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.02,0:22:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不需要做這種解釋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.09,0:22:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,我已經…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.73,0:22:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對妳,我對妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.03,0:22:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有感覺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.70,0:22:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.56,0:22:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管…管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.03,0:22:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要在意我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.83,0:22:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.14,0:22:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在你身邊,你也不要緊是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.21,0:23:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.61,0:23:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她為什麼要哭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.38,0:23:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.76,0:23:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員要去旅行?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.29,0:23:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對,一個女人自己去旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.76,0:23:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不追去不要緊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.00,0:23:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.87,0:23:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.60,0:24:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『五代快追上去\N響子失戀的隻身之旅』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.24,0:24:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等等我,我一定會追上妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.26,0:24:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人坐在黎明的護欄上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.80,0:24:45.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今一直在尋找遺落愛的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.39,0:24:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.72,0:24:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…一陣風…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.16,0:25:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目光交會…只有…再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.27,0:25:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…現在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.37,0:25:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…在雨中…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.74,0:25:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忽然…胸口…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.11,0:25:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢…濡濕而發光
